  "title": "Junior Relationship Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description & Requirements</strong></p><p>We are seeking a self driven and detail-oriented Junior Relationship Manager to support our Relationship Managers in managing UHNI/HNI client portfolios and ensuring high service standards. This role is ideal for candidates passionate about financial markets and looking to develop their expertise in a client-facing, private banking environment.</p><p>Salary: SGD 4 – 5.5k</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p>1. Assist Relationship Managers in servicing UHNI/HNI clients by addressing day-to-day queries and maintaining overall client satisfaction.</p><p>2. Facilitate client onboarding, review documentation, and ensure compliance with regulatory and internal standards.</p><p>3. Conduct portfolio monitoring, prepare briefings and reports as required, and coordinate with internal departments for smooth client delivery.</p><p>4. Identify client needs and recommend appropriate solutions or investment products.</p><p>5. Ensure adherence to legal, regulatory, and risk management standards in all client interactions.</p><p>6. Contribute to business development and support ongoing growth initiatives of the team.</p><p><strong>Candidate Profile & Qualities</strong></p><ol><li>0-1 years of relevant experience in private banking or wealth management.</li><li>Candidates must have completed their graduation through a full-time, regular program from a recognized university.</li><li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills with a client-centric approach.</li><li>High attention to detail, with the ability to multitask and work collaboratively across teams.</li></ol><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted for the next steps.</p>",
